        "fileKey": "scriptjs",
        "contents": "let factorial = (n) => n <= 1 ? BigInt(n) : BigInt(n) * BigInt(factorial(--n));\n\nlet sumDigits = n => n.toString().split('').map(x => parseInt(x)).reduce((a,b) => a + b);\n\nfunction sumFactorialDigits(n) {\n  return sumDigits(factorial(n));\n}",
